@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lvbehq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.39 + v1 + 0.09)) / wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.60)))
    v1 = wp.exp(v2)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.sin(v0))
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = 0.82
    tmp = v2
    tmp = wp.cos((wp.abs(v0 + 0.34) + (v1 + 0.68 - v2 + 0.79)))
    data[tid] = v0
